{"tid":1899591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江省疾控中心: 茶水可殺滅並有效抑制細胞內新型冠狀病毒複製","createTime":"2020-02-26T17:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T05:08:31.000Z","uid":89543,"like":42,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"4b63d00892534ebd405eb1aadbe4d4668d4b2bdd","tid":1899591,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"來源：浙江省疾控中心官方微信<br />\n<br />\n權威發布<br />\n<br />\n在省科技廳《新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情防控關鍵技術的研究》重大專項的支持下，浙江省疾病預防控制中心研究人員盧亦愚、馮燕等專家發布最新研究成果：日常的飲用茶水在細胞水平具有抗新型冠狀病毒的作用。<br />\n<br />\n研究組選擇了綠茶、鐵觀音與大紅袍，稱取上述各類茶葉2克，用50mL開水（實測90℃）浸泡30min，此時濃度計為40 mg/mL（即通常泡茶時的頭道茶水），冷卻至室溫後，用細胞維持液稀釋至各實驗濃度。<br />\n<br />\n首先，以不同濃度的茶水（2.5-10 mg/mL）進行體外殺滅病毒試驗，將開水與市售飲用水設置為實驗對照組。不同濃度茶水，以及對照組與100TCID50的新型冠狀病毒分別作用1小時後，感染Vero細胞並培養48 小時，測定各組的病毒核酸增殖水平。<br />\n<br />\n結果表明，與未經茶水處理的病毒對照組比較，茶水處理組新型冠狀病毒的核酸增殖量降低了1萬-10萬倍；而用於沖泡的開水、市售飲用水對照組，其增殖狀況與病毒對照組一致，提示茶水對新型冠狀病毒具有良好的細胞外殺滅效果。其次，研究組還採用0.25~2 mg/mL的茶水對新型冠狀病毒感染1小時後的細胞進行處理，培養48小時後，發現0.25 mg/mL的綠茶，1~2 mg/mL的大紅袍和0.5~1 mg/mL的鐵觀音均具有抑制新型冠狀病毒複製的能力，抑制效果隨茶水濃度上升而提高。<br />\n<br />\n本研究首次發現以茶多酚（包括兒茶素）為主體的茶水，在體外培養細胞中，對新型冠狀病毒具有良好的細胞外殺滅與細胞內增殖抑製作用。<br />\n<br />\n茶飲料是我國上千年來一直使用的具有防病、治病與養生的健康飲料，因此研究組認為喝茶可能會有益於新冠肺炎的預防。<br />\n<br />\n來源：中心微生物所<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-26/detail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgn%2F2020-02-26%2Fdetail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ef71f262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-26/detail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html?from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"95bcaf0cd1a47c89dfa232a917ebe38c5add24ab","tid":1899591,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f45013c1d7e6206d1396ab6a968bae4695bfcc","tid":1899591,"uid":258566,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce758fbeca70adca5e6576e2bc4809d8d6c2d7e1","tid":1899591,"uid":104138,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"on9 , 酒精直頭殺埋隻毒tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f812bd4b305bf0f75d1161684b00162ab976ed2e","tid":1899591,"uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f45013c1d7e6206d1396ab6a968bae4695bfcc","tid":1899591,"uid":258566,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28371a5a1e544c676f5f5270c769303302f26d96","tid":1899591,"uid":129,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"On9...你試下用熱水啦不如"},{"pid":"3105d9f39dcc5d628f99c52b9db06626d944de57","tid":1899591,"uid":68290,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:08:44.000Z","msg":"......即係你諗住用茶灌落肺入面咁醫病人？"},{"pid":"8228cd77f1c0e4a6afc92406bd13edd4f790d8d0","tid":1899591,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:08:45.000Z","msg":"津路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5382f0ba4bdeb55fcaac7267ed0febe0f851193d","tid":1899591,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"屌你唔好再細啲.jpg"},{"pid":"9825df4198cb6dd6e96138cfb8fa8ce71ff6ad2e","tid":1899591,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"香爐灰效果可能仲好喎"},{"pid":"8a8542f43b75a0a61b7405f3ba45492d647848b4","tid":1899591,"uid":79137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"灌茶入肺<br />\n將D茶打入血管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5073b59bb9ca1081adddbf3ceca24ff0a03a8324","tid":1899591,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:11:21.000Z","msg":"綠茶抗癌？"},{"pid":"1db3cb894dbd31cabd530937f0d85efefcb15086","tid":1899591,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"用火都得"},{"pid":"a938524aae0397e4d54abbf7c0df703fd69c3505","tid":1899591,"uid":8880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"支持飲茶醫病 大力推廣俾廣大中國人 飲茶唔洗怕感染 可以照常生活"},{"pid":"42d7e1e0d0fed7cb0db0f6cfee4a7624e7674e25","tid":1899591,"uid":263183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"康師傅冰紅茶有無上市"},{"pid":"12e8ccf08b6a55d644f3a300a1c9dc2d5d93993d","tid":1899591,"uid":264726,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"4b63d00892534ebd405eb1aadbe4d4668d4b2bdd","tid":1899591,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"來源：浙江省疾控中心官方微信<br />\n<br />\n權威發布<br />\n<br />\n在省科技廳《新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情防控關鍵技術的研究》重大專項的支持下，浙江省疾病預防控制中心研究人員盧亦愚、馮燕等專家發布最新研究成果：日常的飲用茶水在細胞水平具有抗新型冠狀病毒的作用。<br />\n<br />\n研究組選擇了綠茶、鐵觀音與大紅袍，稱取上述各類茶葉2克，用50mL開水（實測90℃）浸泡30min，此時濃度計為40 mg/mL（即通常泡茶時的頭道茶水），冷卻至室溫後，用細胞維持液稀釋至各實驗濃度。<br />\n<br />\n首先，以不同濃度的茶水（2.5-10 mg/mL）進行體外殺滅病毒試驗，將開水與市售飲用水設置為實驗對照組。不同濃度茶水，以及對照組與100TCID50的新型冠狀病毒分別作用1小時後，感染Vero細胞並培養48 小時，測定各組的病毒核酸增殖水平。<br />\n<br />\n結果表明，與未經茶水處理的病毒對照組比較，茶水處理組新型冠狀病毒的核酸增殖量降低了1萬-10萬倍；而用於沖泡的開水、市售飲用水對照組，其增殖狀況與病毒對照組一致，提示茶水對新型冠狀病毒具有良好的細胞外殺滅效果。其次，研究組還採用0.25~2 mg/mL的茶水對新型冠狀病毒感染1小時後的細胞進行處理，培養48小時後，發現0.25 mg/mL的綠茶，1~2 mg/mL的大紅袍和0.5~1 mg/mL的鐵觀音均具有抑制新型冠狀病毒複製的能力，抑制效果隨茶水濃度上升而提高。<br />\n<br />\n本研究首次發現以茶多酚（包括兒茶素）為主體的茶水，在體外培養細胞中，對新型冠狀病毒具有良好的細胞外殺滅與細胞內增殖抑製作用。<br />\n<br />\n茶飲料是我國上千年來一直使用的具有防病、治病與養生的健康飲料，因此研究組認為喝茶可能會有益於新冠肺炎的預防。<br />\n<br />\n來源：中心微生物所<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-26/detail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgn%2F2020-02-26%2Fdetail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ef71f262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-26/detail-iimxyqvz6004629.d.html?from=wap</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"注意係「體外殺滅病毒試驗」<br />\n<br />\n病毒喺細胞之外本來就好脆弱，同喺細胞入面嘅病毒係兩回事。細胞外消滅到病毒，唔代表喺細胞入面都消滅到。<br />\n<br />\n又假設喺細胞入面一樣消滅到病毒，但就咁浸就消滅到病毒嘅液體，要幾多有幾多，問題係用唔用到喺醫療上？假設消滅病毒嘅原來係佢所講嘅茶多酚，咁點樣將啲茶多酚送到去細胞入面？飲落肚？經消化作用轉化，會變咗做乜？進入血液，又有幾多去到細胞？<br />\n<br />\n成日都聽到呢樣嘢殺到癌細胞，嗰樣嘢消滅到咩細菌病毒，到頭來從來都唔見有產品出現，就係咁解。"},{"pid":"81ec31004d91caca69e93f2559ff66d9982bfad6","tid":1899591,"uid":350267,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲19 In vitro實驗 我用手槍打爆個培養皿我都可以話殺到病毒啦"},{"pid":"1d529c67e5608eca9bc4e9add10768731d691ca8","tid":1899591,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81ec31004d91caca69e93f2559ff66d9982bfad6","tid":1899591,"uid":350267,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲19 In vitro實驗 我用手槍打爆個培養皿我都可以話殺到病毒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f5693a5575e85bc404fb783dababd3641df5fd","tid":1899591,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"建議用紅水殺菌"},{"pid":"b83094012d997c08447e676c3dc1607660b16866","tid":1899591,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"口水更有效"},{"pid":"398e25759f11a83d93fb5bc532cd0c97636a32f7","tid":1899591,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de823371e29e9